author: Chris Thompson

text: The Solar Quote: s website provides believable and reliable information. The 3 suppliers seemed to genuinely want to offer solutions suitable for my circumstance. Interestingly, there was a diversity of proposals, all of which could fall into a style of accepted wisdom, but I chose one which suited my line of thinking on design.
